Let me look at how existing kabigon code accesses fields. Looking at itKabigon_UnkMotion0_Anim asm, it accesses 0xE34 which is `pokemon.timer`. Let me also check the specialAttributes — at 0x14 that's `itPokemonAttributes.x14` which is `s32`.

